snippet: Agnieszka Radwanska beat fourth-seeded Petra Kvitova, 6-2, 4-6, 6-3, at the WTA Finals in Singapore on Sunday to clinch the biggest title of her career.
abstract: Agnieszka Radwanska defeats Petra Kvitova to win WTA Finals; other tennis matches noted.
lead_paragraph: Agnieszka Radwanska beat fourth-seeded Petra Kvitova, 6-2, 4-6, 6-3, at the WTA Finals in Singapore on Sunday to clinch the biggest title of her career.

headline.main: Radwanska Wins Title at WTA Finals
